\":\"1280*720\",\"description\":\"The size of the generated media in pixels (width*height).\",\"enum\":[\"1280*720\",\"720*1280\"],\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"prompt\",\"image\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"prompt\",\"image\",\"negative_prompt\",\"size\",\"num_inference_steps\",\"duration\",\"guidance_scale\",\"flow_shift\",\"seed\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.704', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.704', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.704');
