-maverick\",\"meta-llama/llama-4-scout\"],\"x-ui-component\":\"command\"},\"priority\":{\"default\":\"latency\",\"description\":\"Throughput is the default and is recommended for most use cases. Latency is recommended for use cases where low latency is important.\",\"enum\":[\"throughput\",\"latency\"],\"title\":\"Priority\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"prompt\":{\"description\":\"The positive prompt for the generation.\",\"maxLength\":10000,\"title\":\"Prompt\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"reasoning\":{\"default\":false,\"description\":\"Should reasoning be the part of the final answer.\",\"title\":\"Reasoning\",\"type\":\"boolean\"},\"system_prompt\":{\"description\":\"System prompt to provide context or instructions to the model\",\"title\":\"System Prompt\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"temperature\":{\"description\":\"This setting influences the variety in the model’s responses. Lower values lead to more predictable and typical responses, while higher values encourage more diverse and less common responses. At 0, the model always gives the same response for a given input.\",\"maximum\":2,\"minimum\":0,\"title\":\"Temperature\",\"type\":\"number\"}},\"required\":[\"prompt\"],\"title\":\"ChatInput\",\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"prompt\",\"system_prompt\",\"reasoning\",\"priority\",\"temperature\",\"max_tokens\",\"model\",\"enable_sync_mode\"]}}]}', '{\"model_id\":\"wavespeed-ai/any-llm\",\"name\":\"wavespeed-ai/any-llm\",\"base_price\":0.001,\"formula\":\"{\\\"total_price\\\": base_price + (model = \\\"google/gemini-3-flash-preview\\\" ? 30000 : 0)}\",\"description\":\"Any LLM is a versatile large language model for text generation, comprehension, and diverse NLP tasks such as chat and summarization. Ready-to-use REST inference API, best performance, no coldstarts, affordable pricing.\",\"type\":\"llm\",\"sort_order\":100,\"api_schema\":{\"api_schemas\":[{\"type\":\"model_run\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"server\":\"https://api.wavespeed.ai\",\"api_path\":\"/api/v3/waves