ical position. Values are rounded to the nearest valid angle: -30 (low angle), 0 (eye level), 30 (elevated), 60 (high angle).\",\"maximum\":60,\"minimum\":-30,\"type\":\"integer\",\"x-ui-component\":\"slider\"}},\"required\":[\"images\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"images\",\"horizontal_angle\",\"vertical_angle\",\"distance\",\"prompt\",\"size\",\"seed\",\"output_format\",\"enable_base64_output\",\"enable_sync_mode\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.039', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.039', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.039');
