onent\":\"uploader\"},\"voice\":{\"description\":\"Voice reference. Must be a .wav or .mp3 file longer than 15 seconds. If only a voice reference is given, an a cappella vocal hum will be generated.\",\"format\":\"uri\",\"type\":\"string\",\"x-accept\":\"audio/mp3,audio/wav\",\"x-ui-component\":\"uploader\"}},\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"lyrics\",\"bitrate\",\"sample_rate\",\"song\",\"voice\",\"instrumental\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.415', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.415', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.415');
