2. Supports single or multiple product images; 3. Best for front-facing human figures with simple poses and clear photos; 4. Images can be provided via URLs or Base64 encode; 5. Supported codecs: PNG, JPEG, JPG, WebP; 6. Image aspect ratio must be less than 1:4 or 4:1; 7. Maximum file size: 50MB; 8. Base64 decode length must be under 50MB with appropriate content type string.\",\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"image\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"image\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.360', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.360', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.360');
