textarea\"},\"video\":{\"description\":\"Input video URL for question answering. Supports common video formats (MP4, MOV, WebM). Maximum 2 minutes.\",\"format\":\"uri\",\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"video\",\"text\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"video\",\"text\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.817', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.817', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.817');
