ugh the API.\",\"disabled\":true,\"type\":\"boolean\"},\"guidance_scale\":{\"default\":3.5,\"description\":\"The guidance scale to use for the generation.\",\"maximum\":20,\"minimum\":1,\"step\":0.1,\"type\":\"number\"},\"image\":{\"description\":\"The image to generate an image from.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"mask_image\":{\"description\":\"The mask image tells the model where to generate new pixels (white) and where to preserve the original image (black). It acts as a stencil or guide for targeted image editing.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"num_images\":{\"default\":1,\"description\":\"The number of images to generate.\",\"maximum\":4,\"minimum\":1,\"type\":\"integer\"},\"num_inference_steps\":{\"default\":28,\"description\":\"The number of inference steps to perform.\",\"maximum\":50,\"minimum\":1,\"type\":\"integer\"},\"output_format\":{\"default\":\"jpeg\",\"description\":\"The format of the output image.\",\"enum\":[\"jpeg\",\"png\",\"webp\"],\"type\":\"string\"},\"prompt\":{\"description\":\"The positive prompt for the generation.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"seed\":{\"default\":-1,\"description\":\"The random seed to use for the generation. -1 means a random seed will be used.\",\"type\":\"integer\"},\"size\":{\"default\":\"1024*1024\",\"description\":\"The size of the generated media in pixels (width*height).\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"strength\":{\"default\":0.8,\"description\":\"Strength indicates extent to transform the reference image.\",\"maximum\":1,\"minimum\":0,\"step\":0.01,\"type\":\"number\"}},\"required\":[\"prompt\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"prompt\",\"image\",\"mask_image\",\"strength\",\"size\",\"num_inference_steps\",\"seed\",\"guidance_scale\",\"num_images\",\"output_format\",\"enable_base64_output\",\"enable_sync_mode\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.411', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.411', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.411');
