yle guidance, and context-aware improvements. Open-source vision-language model. Ready-to-use REST API, no cold starts, affordable pricing.\",\"type\":\"llm\",\"sort_order\":100,\"api_schema\":{\"api_schemas\":[{\"type\":\"model_run\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"server\":\"https://api.wavespeed.ai\",\"api_path\":\"/api/v3/wavespeed-ai/molmo2/prompt-optimizer\",\"request_schema\":{\"properties\":{\"enable_sync_mode\":{\"default\":false,\"description\":\"If set to true, the function will wait for the result to be generated and uploaded before returning the response. It allows you to get the result directly in the response. This property is only available through the API.\",\"disabled\":true,\"type\":\"boolean\"},\"image\":{\"description\":\"Image to use as context for prompt optimization.\",\"format\":\"uri\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"mode\":{\"default\":\"image\",\"description\":\"The aim of the optimization, either for image or video generation.\",\"enum\":[\"image\",\"video\"],\"type\":\"string\"},\"style\":{\"default\":\"default\",\"description\":\"Style or tone to apply to the optimized prompt.\",\"enum\":[\"default\",\"artistic\",\"photographic\",\"technical\",\"anime\",\"realistic\"],\"type\":\"string\"},\"text\":{\"description\":\"Text to expand or use as context for prompt optimization.\",\"type\":\"string\",\"x-ui-component\":\"textarea\"}},\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"image\",\"text\",\"style\",\"mode\",\"enable_sync_mode\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.824', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.824', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.824');
