iption\":\"The mask image to indicate the area to be erased. The area to be erased should be in white color and the area to be kept should be in black color.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"prompt\":{\"description\":\"The text prompt for specifying the objects or areas to be removed from the video.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"video\":{\"description\":\"The video for generating the output.\",\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"video\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"video\",\"prompt\",\"mask_image\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.935', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.935', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.935');
