ng vs 2.1 Std. Ready-to-use REST inference API, best performance, no coldstarts, affordable pricing.\",\"type\":\"image-to-video\",\"sort_order\":3200,\"api_schema\":{\"api_schemas\":[{\"type\":\"model_run\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"server\":\"https://api.wavespeed.ai\",\"api_path\":\"/api/v3/kwaivgi/kling-v2.5-turbo-std/image-to-video\",\"request_schema\":{\"properties\":{\"duration\":{\"default\":5,\"description\":\"The duration of the generated media in seconds.\",\"enum\":[5,10],\"type\":\"integer\",\"x-ui-component\":\"select\"},\"guidance_scale\":{\"default\":0.5,\"description\":\"The guidance scale to use for the generation.\",\"maximum\":1,\"minimum\":0,\"step\":0.01,\"type\":\"number\"},\"image\":{\"description\":\"First frame of the video; Supported image formats include.jpg/.jpeg/.png; The image file size cannot exceed 10MB, and the image resolution should not be less than 300*300px, and the aspect ratio of the image should be between 1:2.5 ~ 2.5:1.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"negative_prompt\":{\"description\":\"The negative prompt for the generation.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"prompt\":{\"description\":\"The positive prompt for the generation.\",\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"prompt\",\"image\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"prompt\",\"image\",\"negative_prompt\",\"guidance_scale\",\"duration\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.843', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.843', '2026-06-09 08:56:05.843');
