pported image formats include.jpg/.jpeg/.png; The image file size cannot exceed 10MB, and the image resolution should not be less than 300*300px, and the aspect ratio of the image should be between 1:2.5 ~ 2.5:1.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"negative_prompt\":{\"description\":\"The negative prompt for the generation.\",\"maxLength\":2048,\"type\":\"string\"},\"resolution\":{\"default\":\"540p\",\"description\":\"Video quality (360p/540p/720p/1080p).\",\"enum\":[\"360p\",\"540p\",\"720p\",\"1080p\"],\"type\":\"string\",\"x-ui-component\":\"select\"},\"thinking_type\":{\"default\":\"auto\",\"description\":\"Prompt reasoning enhancement. Controls whether the system should enhance your prompt with internal reasoning and optimization. \\\"enabled\\\" : Turn on system-level optimization. \\\"disabled\\\" : Turn off system-level optimization. \\\"auto\\\" or omitted: Let the model decide automatically\",\"enum\":[\"enabled\",\"disabled\",\"auto\"],\"type\":\"string\",\"x-ui-component\":\"select\"}},\"required\":[\"effect\",\"image\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"image\",\"effect\",\"resolution\",\"duration\",\"negative_prompt\",\"thinking_type\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.669', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.669', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.669');
