ng the output.\",\"type\":\"string\"},\"prompt\":{\"description\":\"The positive prompt for the generation.\",\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"prompt\",\"image\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"prompt\",\"image\",\"duration\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.337', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.337', '2026-06-09 08:56:06.337');
