Will\",\"Jessica\",\"Eric\",\"Chris\",\"Brian\",\"Daniel\",\"Lily\",\"Bill\"],\"x-placeholder\":\"Please input your custom voice ID\",\"x-ui-component\":\"command\"}},\"required\":[\"text\",\"voice_id\"],\"type\":\"object\",\"x-order-properties\":[\"text\",\"voice_id\",\"similarity\",\"stability\",\"use_speaker_boost\"]}}]}}', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.076', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.076', '2026-06-09 08:56:07.076');
